This paper deals with a production recommender system that uses machine learning algorithms to learn from logged implicit feedback. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), and Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC).
